  "title": "PROJECT ADMIN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>· Keeps track of project control/monitoring documents and files and circulate those documents.</p><p>· Collect and store the project completion documents.</p><p>· Arrange and support the relevant department to execute the meeting.</p><p>· Prepare the documents, charts and presentation as per request from Project Manager.</p><p>· Manage the I/O for the external correspondences.</p><p>· Registration and distribution of drawings/documents issued.</p><p>· Update status of all documentations in share folder.</p><p>· Necessary documentation for ISO auditing.</p><p>· Provide administration support.</p><p>· Handle general administrative duties.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p><p>· Diploma holder in business administration / construction management or other relevant disciplines</p><p>· Minimum 2 years of document control working experience in the construction industry</p><p>· Good communication skills</p><p>· Proficient in MS Office</p><p>· Knowledge of DAR / Insight is an advantage</p><p>· Location: East</p>",
